## ğŸš€ Features

âœ… Play `.wav` files instantly  
âœ… Generate and play sounds directly from **NumPy arrays**  
âœ… Near-zero latency and minimal CPU usage thanks to **Rust**  
âœ… Safe, stable, and cross-platform  
âœ… Async-ready design for future streaming  

